cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use RaceLLM in your research or work, please cite it using this metadata."
type: software
title: RaceLLM
abstract: >
  RaceLLM is a Go CLI that fans out a single prompt to multiple LLM providers
  simultaneously (OpenAI, Anthropic, Gemini, Ollama), streams all responses in
  parallel, and surfaces timing results through a live BubbleTea TUI dashboard.
  It supports two race modes: "all" (wait for every provider) and "fastest"
  (cancel the rest once the first completes).
